## Day-to-Day Workflow

```
git checkout main && git pull
git checkout -b feature/my-feature

# ... develop ...

/pre-commit                          # guardian consistency check
git add -p && git commit -m "feat: ..."

/review src/path/to/changed          # deep review before PR
/pr                                  # lint → commit → push → open PR

# merge on GitHub

git checkout main && git pull
/run-jobs "PR merged #N"             # sync roadmap + docs
```

## Claude Code Skills

| Command | What it does |
|---------|-------------|
| `/setup` | Bootstrap plugin structure (run once on new projects) |
| `/pm` | Project status: branches, job queue, roadmap |
| `/pm-update-roadmap` | Sync roadmap after a PR merges |
| `/pm-sync` | Sync issues to Notion (if configured) |
| `/architect [feature]` | Design a feature before building it |
| `/create-job [task]` | Queue a unit of work in jobs/pending/ |
| `/run-jobs` | Execute next unblocked job |
| `/review [path]` | Deep code review |
| `/pre-commit` | Quick consistency check before committing |
| `/pr` | Ship: lint → commit → push → open PR |
| `/audit` | Full codebase audit, generate issue reports |

## Full Job Workflow

```
/architect feature description    # design + roadmap entry
/create-job 'task description'    # queue implementation job
/run-jobs                         # pick up and execute job
/pr                               # ship the branch
/run-jobs "PR merged #N"          # sync docs after merge
```
